            <form>
               <orth>crag (cnag)</orth>
            </form>
            <def>made from a piece of tree trunk shaped like a modern pouffe but smaller and used for sitting by the fire.</def>
         </entry>
         <ab type="heading"
             xml:id="HouseandFurnishings_DunoonJMacLeantaigh-d0e911"
             subtype="h1">7. Sobhal, bàthach, no bothanan sam bith eile</ab>
         <entry xml:id="HouseandFurnishings_DunoonJMacLeantaigh-d0e916">
            <form>
               <orth>bàthach</orth>
            </form>
            <def>byre.</def>
         </entry>
         <entry xml:id="HouseandFurnishings_DunoonJMacLeantaigh-d0e925">
            <form>
